name: openmage-module-fostering/parcelpro_carrier
description: Parcel Pro for Magento is a web-based Insured Shipping solution that integrates with your Magento online store, adding Parcel Pro as one of your shipping options. It allows you to set the price of shipping and insurance coverage quickly and easily.

authors.name: Parcel Pro, Inc. Joey Chan, Project Lead Jasper Lynn, Project Manager
